<div class="card form"><h2>步数提交</h2><p class="muted">旧版 Zepp/小米运动接口入口已保留，但当前暂不支持同步。</p><form method="post"><input type="hidden" name="mode" value="sync"><label>Zepp / 小米运动账号</label><input name="sport_username" placeholder="请输入账号"><label>密码</label><input name="sport_password" type="password" placeholder="请输入密码"><label>目标步数</label><input name="target_steps" type="number" min="0" max="200000" placeholder="例如 8000"><p><button class="btn">提交步数</button></p></form></div><div class="card form"><h2>本站步数记录</h2><p class="muted">这里记录你自己的每日步数，仅保存在本站。</p><form method="post"><input type="hidden" name="mode" value="record"><label>日期</label><input name="record_date" type="date" value="<?=date('Y-m-d')?>"><label>步数</label><input name="steps" type="number" min="0" max="200000" placeholder="例如 8000"><label>备注</label><input name="note" maxlength="255" placeholder="可选"><p><button class="btn green">保存记录</button></p></form></div><div class="card"><h3>最近记录</h3><?php if(empty($records)): ?><p class="muted">暂无记录。</p><?php else: ?><div class="table-wrap"><table><tr><th>日期</th><th>步数</th><th>备注</th><th>更新时间</th></tr><?php foreach($records as $r): ?><tr><td><?=h($r['record_date'])?></td><td><b><?=h($r['steps'])?></b></td><td><?=h($r['note']?:'-')?></td><td><?=h($r['updated_at']?:$r['created_at'])?></td></tr><?php endforeach; ?></table></div><?php endif; ?></div>